data.description: Welcome to this exquisite 5 bedroom, 3 bath home situated on a sprawling 3.75 acre lot in school district 6, offering the perfect blend of tranquility and elegance.  This move-in ready home features a cozy living room with a gas logs fireplace, seamlessly connected to the breakfast area and kitchen, perfect for gatherings and everyday living. The owner's suite offers a luxurious ensuite bathroom and 2 spacious walk-in closets, providing a private retreat within the home. The additional bedrooms are equally welcoming, ensuring comfort for all residents or guests. . This home has everything you could need for quiet, country living while still maintaining access to the conveniences of all that Spartanburg has to offer. Call today for your private showing!
